race.description: Glass Warrior Ambassador For Nets Plate Hcp
race.comment: VERBANO (4) delivered in a 72 here third-up over 1400m finding more like her best. Came hard after settling back from the wide gate. Has her first crack at a mile and on what we saw last time she should manage it comfortably. Gets in light again with the 2kg claim. ORIGINAL GLAZE (5) also peaks and improved again beaten 2.3L behind SHY GUY. She sits down in the weights as well and has to be considered. SHY GUY (1) made it back-to-back wins in that contest. Has to lug 3kg more today, but the hat-trick can't be ruled out. METAVERSE (2) drops back from a middle distance on a 7-day return. It's an ask but he'll be fitter and rates a hope.
